You have used getenforce to verify that the current mode is Enforcing and need tochange certain rules in real time. Which command can be used for this purpose?
A)  systemd- selinux
B)  sechange
C)  semanage
D)  setsepol
C
C. The semanage command can be used to make changes such as ports, booleans, andcontexts in order to keep a policy in Enforcing mode but still make changes. The othercommands shown are not valid for this purpose.Chapter 3: Scripting, Containers, and Automation (Domain 3.0)211
